Class GraphQlRSocketAutoConfiguration

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.graphql.rsocket.GraphQlRSocketAutoConfiguration
@AutoConfiguration(after={GraphQlAutoConfiguration.class,RSocketMessagingAutoConfiguration.class}) @ConditionalOnClass({graphql.GraphQL.class,org.springframework.graphql.execution.GraphQlSource.class,io.rsocket.core.RSocketServer.class,reactor.netty.http.server.HttpServer.class}) @ConditionalOnBean({org.springframework.messaging.rsocket.annotation.support.RSocketMessageHandler.class,org.springframework.graphql.data.method.annotation.support.AnnotatedControllerConfigurer.class}) @ConditionalOnProperty(prefix="spring.graphql.rsocket", name="mapping") public class GraphQlRSocketAutoConfiguration extends Object
